    "Additionally, there may be legal issues such as copyright and authorship status to consider.",
    "Interpretability issues are also a concern, as it can be challenging to interpret the outputs generated by Chat GPT.There is also a risk of referencing issues, where Chat GPT may generate content that is not properly cited or attributed.",
